description:
In this lecture, Pastor Randy Skeete reveals the common theme that binds all of Creation together, animate and inanimate, animal and human: Gods law. All matter in the universe is under physical law. Since humans, however, are not just physical creatures but moral creatures made in Gods image, we are also governed by moral laws, which God gave us in the Ten Commandments. Find out how Gods law governs everything in the universe, and how our obedience to His law results in harmony not only with the natural universe, but with God Himself. This lecture reminds us that to love God is to obey Him, and obeying God means obeying His law.

Discover more: 
http://amazingdiscoveries.org
